Replace the audience filter (sectors, sizes, locations) on a lens. Body is the full `Filter` object — this is a REPLACE, not a merge. Returns 400 `default_lens` if applied to the org default lens (clone it first). `dry_run:true` returns the call shape without contacting the backend.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} low-level mutation when you've already prepared the merged filter.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} from agent flow — use leadbay_adjust_audience, which handles draft-vs-direct routing, permission fallback, and the merge logic so unrelated criteria aren't dropped.

{{include:headers/verification-required-if-write}}
